data.description: 3736 Grace Falls Dr. Wonderful home, that has all bedrooms upstairs, as well as a spacious bonus area. Downstairs has Living room, separate dining room and kitchen with ample space for table and chairs. The following updates have been completed within the last 2 years!! New Roof, both HVAC systems, Water Heater and Fence. Home is truly ready to go! 15 Minutes to the awesome new Tanger Outlets, minutes to several lake access points, 20-25 minutes to BNA, The Avenue Murfreesboro and downtown. Home is currently leased and we will need 24hr notice for showings. Home Warranty included!
